Class FrontierImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dice_research.squirrel.frontier.impl.FrontierImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class FrontierImpl
extends Object
implements org.dice_research.squirrel.frontier.Frontier
    Standard implementation of the Frontier interface containing a queue and a uriFilter.

    Michael Röder (roeder@informatik.uni-leipzig.de)
